{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/java/basic_java/3_Layered_Architecture/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Iol-lshh's"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"aca95404-75af-5d2a-ae37-68b9cfd8fdcb","excerpt":"**Martin Fowler의 \"엔터프라이즈 애플리케이션 아키텍처 패턴\"**에 따르면, 소프트웨어는 계층화된 구조를 통해 복잡성을 관리합니다. 상위 계층은 하위 계층의 서비스를 활용하지만, 하위 계층은 상위 계층을 인식하지 않습니다. 3.1. 3계층 시스템의 구성 3.1.1.…","html":"<ul>\n<li>**Martin Fowler의 \"엔터프라이즈 애플리케이션 아키텍처 패턴\"**에 따르면, 소프트웨어는 계층화된 구조를 통해 복잡성을 관리합니다.</li>\n<li><strong>상위 계층</strong>은 하위 계층의 서비스를 활용하지만, <strong>하위 계층</strong>은 상위 계층을 인식하지 않습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>3.1. 3계층 시스템의 구성</h2>\n<h3>3.1.1. 3계층의 주요 구성</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>프레젠테이션 계층 (Presentation layer)</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>사용자 인터페이스를 담당하며, 애플리케이션의 기능과 데이터를 표시합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@RestController</span>\n<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@RequestMapping</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/products\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductController</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductService</span> service\n\t\n    <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@GetMapping</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"/{id}\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductDto</span> <span class=\"token function\">getProduct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@PathVariable</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Long</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> service<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getProduct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><strong>비즈니스 로직 계층 (Business logic layer)</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>애플리케이션의 핵심 로직을 처리.</li>\n<li>의사 결정, 계산, 데이터 처리 등을 포함.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Service</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductService</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductRepository</span> repository<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductDto</span> <span class=\"token function\">getProduct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Long</span> id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">Product</span> product <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> repository<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProductDto</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">from</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>product<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>데이터 접근 계층 (Data access layer)</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>데이터베이스와 상호작용하며 데이터를 저장하고 관리합니다.</li>\n<li>Java의 경우, JPA 또는 Plain Query를 처리하는 레이어의 구현</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/36c33/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.58227848101266%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"       \"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/f058b/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/c26ae/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png 158w,\n/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/6bdcf/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png 315w,\n/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/f058b/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png 630w,\n/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/40601/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png 945w,\n/static/e2863a2e58e7d6ec0e4dafbcce8d606d/36c33/%EC%84%B8%EA%B0%80%EC%A7%80%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94%EA%B3%84%EC%B8%B5.png 946w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><img src=\"./img/Pasted%20image%2020250119160116.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>3.2. MVC 패턴과 3계층 아키텍처의 비교</h2>\n<h3>3.2.1. MVC 패턴</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>사용자 인터페이스 설계에 중점을 둔 패턴으로, 다음 세 가지 구성 요소로 나뉩니다.\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Model</strong>: 비즈니스 로직과 애플리케이션 상태를 정의.</li>\n<li><strong>Controller</strong>: 흐름 제어 및 검증 역할.</li>\n<li><strong>View</strong>: 사용자에게 출력 데이터를 표시.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/7388e/mvc2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.0126582278481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mvc2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/f058b/mvc2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/c26ae/mvc2.png 158w,\n/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/6bdcf/mvc2.png 315w,\n/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/f058b/mvc2.png 630w,\n/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/40601/mvc2.png 945w,\n/static/e52cc9957665c3e28cf90cf973e10a71/7388e/mvc2.png 1104w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>3.2.2. 3계층 아키텍처</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>애플리케이션 전체의 코드 구조를 계층화하여 확장성과 유지보수성을 높이는 것을 목표로 합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>3.3. 도메인 계층의 설계 패턴</h2>\n<h3>3.3.1. 트랜잭션 스크립트</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>특징</strong>: 절차적 방식으로, 각 비즈니스 트랜잭션마다 별도의 스크립트를 작성.</li>\n<li><strong>장점</strong>: 단순하며 데이터 원본 계층과의 연동이 용이.</li>\n<li><strong>단점</strong>: 코드 중복 및 복잡성 증가 가능성.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5a89169af43f589ceaa542cd2f6ea640/9a86a/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.79746835443038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"        \"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5a89169af43f589ceaa542cd2f6ea640/f058b/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5a89169af43f589ceaa542cd2f6ea640/c26ae/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8.png 158w,\n/static/5a89169af43f589ceaa542cd2f6ea640/6bdcf/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8.png 315w,\n/static/5a89169af43f589ceaa542cd2f6ea640/f058b/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8.png 630w,\n/static/5a89169af43f589ceaa542cd2f6ea640/9a86a/%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%9C%EC%9E%AD%EC%85%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8.png 792w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>3.3.2. 도메인 모델</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>특징</strong>: 객체지향적인 접근으로, 각 객체가 관련된 논리를 담당.</li>\n<li><strong>장점</strong>: 복잡한 비즈니스 로직 처리에 적합.</li>\n<li><strong>단점</strong>: 객체 간의 상호작용 이해 및 설계 초기 비용이 높음.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1d090a930e57f2ee2bed365fe6ae9942/c1328/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.36708860759494%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"     \"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1d090a930e57f2ee2bed365fe6ae9942/f058b/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1d090a930e57f2ee2bed365fe6ae9942/c26ae/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8.png 158w,\n/static/1d090a930e57f2ee2bed365fe6ae9942/6bdcf/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8.png 315w,\n/static/1d090a930e57f2ee2bed365fe6ae9942/f058b/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8.png 630w,\n/static/1d090a930e57f2ee2bed365fe6ae9942/c1328/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B8%EB%AA%A8%EB%8D%B8.png 866w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>3.3.3. 테이블 모듈</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>특징</strong>: 레코드 집합과 연동되도록 설계되며, 데이터베이스와의 직접적인 연결에서 효과적.\n<ul>\n<li><strong>차이점</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>도메인 모델은 각 계약마다 객체를 생성.</li>\n<li>테이블 모듈은 인스턴스를 하나만 사용.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6029972c19d22229b8a45c5ab17c104c/c1328/%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.9620253164557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"     \"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6029972c19d22229b8a45c5ab17c104c/f058b/%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6029972c19d22229b8a45c5ab17c104c/c26ae/%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88.png 158w,\n/static/6029972c19d22229b8a45c5ab17c104c/6bdcf/%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88.png 315w,\n/static/6029972c19d22229b8a45c5ab17c104c/f058b/%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88.png 630w,\n/static/6029972c19d22229b8a45c5ab17c104c/c1328/%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%88.png 866w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/19453bb3369196edefbb73e7fbab2fcc/160a3/%EB%8F%84%EB%A9%94%EC%9D%B